todos.title: Prep the vegetables for dinner tonight.
Start studying for your midterm on Wednesday.
I named this Chore Keeper because I've been thinking about buying the game Core Keeper. They sound similar...
This is an app meant to help you keep track of what chores you have to do.
It's made for people like me, who are more responsive to softer visuals that are easier on the eyes when it comes to note-taking and the like.
